title: r/Maliciouscompliance Break Quarantine? Get Arrested!
description:
r/Maliciouscompliance In today's story, OP received very simple and clear instructions from his parents: Don't interfere with our Facebook stuff. So when OP's parents decide to protest the quarantine after they heard about an event on Facebook, OP decides to stay out of it. After all, he's supposed to stay out of their Facebook stuff, right?  Well, his parents get arrested, and suddenly they change their mind and want their son's help again. Sorry, mom and dad, but I can't get involved in your Facebook stuff! If you like this video, subscribe to my channel for more daily Reddit content!

Watch on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LCxuRUIE78k
